headline: NXP Semiconductors N : Simplifies Secure Industrial and IoT Device Authentication with New EdgeLock A30
summary: NXP's new Common Criteria EAL6+ certified EdgeLock A30 secure authenticator combines compatibility with standard MCUs and MPUs, a large memory and EdgeLock 2GO support to deliver an optimized solution...
